code: @Override protected CamelContext createCamelContext() throws Exception {     CamelContext context = super.createCamelContext().     context.addRoutePolicyFactory(new ServiceRegistrationRoutePolicyFactory()).     return context. }

@Override protected RoutesBuilder createRouteBuilder() throws Exception {     return new RouteBuilder() {          @Override         public void configure() throws Exception {             fromF("jetty:http://0.0.0.0:%d/service/endpoint", SERVICE_PORT).routeId(SERVICE_ID).routeGroup(SERVICE_NAME).noAutoStartup().to("log:service-registry?level=INFO").         }     }. }
